      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775782854836,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Creatures:\n- Base Creature\n- Urchin: spawns near \"water\"\n- Fox: spawns near \"forest\"\n- Dinosaur: spawns near both\n- Bird: spawn near tree\n\nTiles:\n- tree\n- water\n- forest\n\nWorld/Map design?\n- make a \"easy\" location\n- - 1 at a time\n- make a \"hard\" location\n- - multiple\n- make a \"death\" location\n- - LOTS\n\nGroup Behaviors:\n- piglins in minecraft\n- - mob mentality\n",
      "fontSize": 55.75843184054832,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Creatures:\n- Base Creature\n- Urchin: spawns near \"water\"\n- Fox: spawns near \"forest\"\n- Dinosaur: spawns near both\n- Bird: spawn near tree\n\nTiles:\n- tree\n- water\n- forest\n\nWorld/Map design?\n- make a \"easy\" location\n- - 1 at a time\n- make a \"hard\" location\n- - multiple\n- make a \"death\" location\n- - LOTS\n\nGroup Behaviors:\n- piglins in minecraft\n- - mob mentality\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
